adjustVertex            Modify given coordinates of given vertices of a
                        simplex
generateVertex          Generates the new vertex of a simplex
labsimplex              Generates simplex object with coordinates of
                        starting vertices.
labsimplex-package      labsimplex: Implementation of simplex
                        optimization algorithms for laboratory
                        applications.
plot.smplx              Makes a two dimentional plot of a simplex
                        object.
plotSimplex3D           Makes a three dimentional plot of a simplex
                        object.
plotSimplexResponse     Plots the response versus the vertex number of
                        a simplex optimization.
print.smplx             Prints given simplex (a 'smplx' class object)
simplexExport           Exports the information contained on a 'smplx'
                        class object.
simplexImport           Imports the information contained in a '.smplx'
                        file.
